# Petropavlovka, Bichursky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Petropavlovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bichursky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 608 as of 2010. There are 6 streets.
Geography
Petropavlovka is located 15&nbsp;km north of Bichura (the district's administrative centre) by road. Altachey is the nearest rural locality.
